Homepage: https://github.com/s0md3v/photon
Description: Lightweight web crawler for OSINT and reconnaissance
 Photon is a fast and lightweight crawler designed to extract
 URLs, files, emails, and other data from web pages for
 OSINT and reconnaissance purposes.
